{"tid":399230,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自家制 carbonara","createTime":"2017-09-13T19:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T12:53:44.000Z","uid":22793,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"380d8e431af5b8abcce4ed9f61b95207b3cd1244","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:02:51.000Z","msg":"Hello 大家好，又係我分享一下煮野心得，唔講咁多，去相<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/024704_1836d46926ae79fec4375c3e1318e7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F024704_1836d46926ae79fec4375c3e1318e7d9.jpg&h=6e013108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料有蛋黃，巴馬臣芝士，意粉，煙肉（正常應該係用pancetta ）用普通煙肉扮住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同cream ,正宗黎講係冇cream既，但我鐘意加兩匙等啲口感creamy 啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025152_1c03713544d07b3fb931b899b188003a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025152_1c03713544d07b3fb931b899b188003a.jpg&h=cae41981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先熱pan加小小油炒香啲煙肉再將多餘油隔走<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025314_8d91d28ba5b3574b691cdf6b27cbf475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025314_8d91d28ba5b3574b691cdf6b27cbf475.jpg&h=b441e23f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後落意粉兜兩兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025435_c7a21a6be1b7cc0b6472ee3ac6de7642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025435_c7a21a6be1b7cc0b6472ee3ac6de7642.jpg&h=948d0002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025436_a242aced42c9af2efddb413078a734bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025436_a242aced42c9af2efddb413078a734bf.jpg&h=0a33dffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再加兩匙更忌廉，芝士我會分2次落，調味我淨係落左小小胡椒，芝士同煙肉都有味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025658_3a8b7e74411cab049967927a685df113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025658_3a8b7e74411cab049967927a685df113.jpg&h=523f49eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025659_25ed03fcb259d500e6c477e5e7d9df90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025659_25ed03fcb259d500e6c477e5e7d9df90.jpg&h=acac46f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到有小小濕濕地就離火落蛋黃，落蛋黃之後就會黏埋一齊就好creamy<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/025833_25d8cdfe2d94a9e26078b2a3997d9af7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F025833_25d8cdfe2d94a9e26078b2a3997d9af7.jpg&h=041e249e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成 Bon app&eacute;tit <br />\n正宗後講係冇cream 既，其實2種方法我都試過，依個人口味啦，如果唔落忌廉可以落小小烚完意粉既水，小tips:落蛋黃前預留返小小濕濕地既狀態，咁加完蛋黃就唔會1pat pat痴埋1舊。<br />\n有機再同大家分享，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fd6a1ba26a4299b31d469a3ff28f77bbd870ff","tid":399230,"uid":40933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5db739f10abd340c32921916399d8a2df3b267","tid":399230,"uid":134799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚夜先黎post"},{"pid":"0450ba2be5f0d98786d27897234812648191b998","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你咁撚夜先黎post</blockquote><br />\nSor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落去7仔叮個carbon食住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d6477dfde38a22d8b514e2a5bef5f2c75b9b4d","tid":399230,"uid":37501,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:20:31.000Z","msg":"條bacon做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5439608bdca27e7c0e7f707bd3b484e9ca5d72a7","tid":399230,"uid":71905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:22:27.000Z","msg":"用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b81f9a58b02afc8cc445910b442282c9566c22","tid":399230,"uid":124700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a14fa3e491a33f8d0e0803cfae481c4e910c35a","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有有試過落cream?"},{"pid":"2658330019435131382a315623ec0834168fe9aa","tid":399230,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:16:10.000Z","msg":"煙肉應該可以爆耐啲 油應該可以唔洗隔<br />\n可能攞佢啲咸香味會更好 有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce559e4d9cd0b3e01698452e733176ea9d2d47d","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煙肉應該可以爆耐啲 油應該可以唔洗隔<br />\n可能攞佢啲咸香味會更好 有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀，爆耐啲會脆啲香口啲，如果用cream就隔油，唔係啲cream就會化開。用水就唔洗仲會香啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd258c07f84d8541de662f914ce47334200ba755","tid":399230,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src