,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3AAdKl1UYZs&d=Q6HFSfryhHplQsGj%2FkHGtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ec23b9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs</a>呢條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你下次試下蛋同芝士唔好撈埋一齊，分開落，落蛋小小水</blockquote><br />\n落<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span>小小水</blockquote><br />\n我唔係好明佢好淡既意思 係蛋味唔夠定係唔夠咸/濃味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9577aa910bb7dbb0b650f5b7e5ae1225682a35","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3AAdKl1UYZs&d=Q6HFSfryhHplQsGj%2FkHGtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ec23b9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs</a>呢條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你下次試下蛋同芝士唔好撈埋一齊，分開落，落蛋小小水</blockquote><br />\n落<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span>小小水</blockquote><br />\n我唔係好明佢好淡既意思 係蛋味唔夠定係唔夠咸/濃味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淡味應該係冇落鹽，不過佢話煙肉好重味，你覺得淡可以落返小小鹽"},{"pid":"08d8d62b86cae0cc1e790b47a0286279338966a8","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:57:34.000Z","msg":"唔夠咸/濃試下落多小小煙肉"},{"pid":"7ec055a661eb411522b44fdb5414