oji\" />"},{"pid":"ac92974239faa9cac6d10f353b0ee7ee2031a841","tid":399230,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:50:29.000Z","msg":"再安全啲係落蛋黃芝士調味落個兜到 煮完先將啲意粉過落去撈？見過好幾條片都係咁教"},{"pid":"c9109a07aa3edf8e0c37c44f14c68ab05aa68411","tid":399230,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再安全啲係落蛋黃芝士調味落個兜到 煮完先將啲意粉過落去撈？見過好幾條片都係咁教</blockquote><br />\n咁做法令蛋黃冇咁快熟，但麻煩小小囉。都可以既"},{"pid":"ff93fa1072ead48879f8129b7145257c22c2af2f","tid":399230,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:16:52.000Z","msg":"其實carbonara 就即係佢地既蛋炒飯<br />\n已經無話正唔正宗"},{"pid":"1ba48b98db8ab1b93792d74cb374cfbe601b1137","tid":399230,"uid":49176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用無落cream既版本成日都失敗，明明跟住youtube做 但係都好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3AAdKl1UYZs&d=Q6HFSfryhHplQsGj%2FkHGtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ec23b9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3AAdKl1UYZs</a>呢條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你下次試下蛋同芝士唔好撈埋一齊，分開落，落蛋小小水</blockquote><br />\n落<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span>小小水</blockquote><br />\n我唔係好明佢好淡既意思 係蛋味唔夠定係唔夠咸/濃味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淡味應該係冇落鹽，不過佢話煙肉好重味，你覺得淡可以落返小小鹽</blockquote><br />\n佢果隻肉真係好撚咸<br />\n同埋我唔中意果隻味"}]}